#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_call_to_action
msgid "2,000 parents<br/> brought their kid to our nursery."
msgstr "2.000 ouders<br/> brachten hun kind naar onze crèche."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        For every kid"
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Voor elk kind"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Open-door policy"
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Open-deur-beleid"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Our mission"
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Onze missie"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_banner
msgid "A little place <br/>of paradise"
msgstr "Een klein stukje <br/>paradijs"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "About us"
msgstr "Over ons"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_image_text
msgid "Activities"
msgstr "Activiteiten"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"All activities are planned to meet each child’s individual needs. This "
"approach will help your child to develop to the best of their ability."
msgstr ""
"Alle activiteiten worden zo gepland dat ze voldoen aan de individuele "
"behoeften van elk kind. Deze aanpak helpt je kind om zich zo goed mogelijk "
"te ontwikkelen."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_call_to_action
msgid "Contact us"
msgstr "Contact"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_kiddo.field_theme_utils__display_name
msgid "Display Name"
msgstr "Schermnaam"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_call_to_action
msgid "Entrust us with your children and go to work with peace of mind"
msgstr "Vertrouw ons je kinderen toe en ga met een gerust gemoed aan het werk"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "Events"
msgstr "Evenementen"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_kiddo.field_theme_utils__id
msgid "ID"
msgstr "ID"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"Our aim is to make the early years of your child’s life as enjoyable, "
"rewarding and positive as possible."
msgstr ""
"We streven ernaar om de eerste levensjaren van je kind zo aangenaam, "
"bevredigend en positief mogelijk te maken."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_banner
msgid ""
"Our goal is to create a safe and nurturing environment for your child to "
"learn and grow. We believe that every child is unique and should be treated "
"as such."
msgstr ""

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "Our team"
msgstr "Ons team"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_image_text
msgid "Our team is composed of experienced nursery nurses."
msgstr "Ons team bestaat uit ervaren kinderverzorgsters."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "Playground"
msgstr "Speelterrein"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model:ir.model,name:theme_kiddo.model_theme_utils
msgid "Theme Utils"
msgstr "Thematools"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_image_text
msgid ""
"They will propose to your children educational activities, playful, varied "
"and adapted to the stage of development."
msgstr ""
"Ze zullen je kinderen gevarieerde, educatieve en leuke activiteiten "
"voorstellen, aangepast aan hun ontwikkelingsfase."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "Visit us"
msgstr "Breng ons een bezoekje"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"You are welcome to come and see the nursery and meet the team at any time "
"convenient to you."
msgstr ""
"Je bent van harte welkom om de crèche te bezoeken en het team te ontmoeten "
"wanneer het jou uitkomt."

#. module: theme_kiddo
